<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="65 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a">你能聽我說嗎～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在
有一個<delay20 />非常大的煩惱<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我最近每一天<delay20 />
都在吃<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本來我是非常喜歡吃的，<delay20 />
但最近不知道為什麼，總覺得有點膩耶～<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我暫時都不想再看到
<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果變成那樣，該怎麼辦才好～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我決定不了
飯後甜點<delay8 />該吃什麼才好～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想吃<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也想吃<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />啊！我想到了！<delay20 />
兩樣都吃就可以了！<10_4 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真是天才～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我每天早上<delay20 />
都會吃麵包<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但今天早上
卻找不到我最愛的果醬，<delay20 />
讓我好煩惱～<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />空瓶子還在，<delay20 />
只有裡面的東西消失了～<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺好像發生了什麼案件喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="66 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<delay8 />昨天晚上<delay20 />
做了一個很棒的夢喔～</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我夢到自己一個人<delay20 />
獨享整個大蛋糕喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是肚子實在太飽了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒辦法吃完。<delay8 />
真是太可惜了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果餓著肚子睡覺的話，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚一定可以看到夢的後續，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我要忍耐，只吃八分飽就好～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在夢裡見到我最愛的奶奶喔～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我奶奶烤的餅乾<delay20 />是人間美味～<pageBreak />我也好想給<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吃吃看喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我夢到自己能在天空自由飛翔喔～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好想試著<delay8 />從天空俯瞰每天生活的<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="33" />喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="0d 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你喔，<delay8 />你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說對著流星許願的話，<delay20 />
願望就會實現喔～</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xe 0xf 0x10" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay20 />要是看到流星的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要許願說：<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「請讓我每天都能吃到<delay20 />
超大<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />吧！」<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我的願望實現了，<delay20 />
一定也會<delay8 />分一點
給<tag a="110" b="4" />吃喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay20 />要是看到流星的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要許願說：<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「請讓我跟<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />的感情<delay8 />
變得更好～」<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想<delay20 />快點看到流星啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呢，<delay20 />要是看到流星的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要許願說：<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「請讓我變身為
帥氣的機器人～」<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為<colour id="3" />機械‧<colour id="65535" /><tag a="110" b="10" />的能量<delay20 />
是好吃的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就拜託你囉～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="67 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呢，<delay8 />只要是交通工具<delay20 />
全都喜歡～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="103_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />汽車就很棒喔～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />悠悠哉哉地兜風感覺很有趣～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呢，<delay20 />只有一次機會也好，<delay8 />　
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想坐一次敞篷車看看啊～！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天氣好的時候，<delay20 />
坐在敞篷車上一定很舒服吧～！<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然下雨的時候會被淋濕就是了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飛機就很棒啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以一下子就飛到<delay8 />
很遠的地方呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我的背上<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也可以有一對<delay8 />
跟飛機一樣帥氣的翅膀就好了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，要是衣服穿不進去的話，
該怎麼辦才好～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />船就很棒啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海面上波光粼粼<delay8 />
一定很漂亮吧～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />起錨～～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />右滿舵！！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是很像船長啊～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="68 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最喜歡畫畫了～<delay frames="40" />
我會用彩色鉛筆、<delay20 />蠟筆、<delay20 />水彩<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />各式各樣的東西來畫畫喔～</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="104_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />彩色鉛筆呀，<delay20 />
柔和的顏色很可愛呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就連削下來的鉛筆屑也是彩色的，<delay20 />
我覺得丟掉太浪費了，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以忍不住<delay8 />把它們收藏起來～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />水彩呀，<delay20 />把顏料調在一起的話，<delay8 />
就會變化出各種不同的顏色，很有趣呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />洗筆桶裡的水的顏色<delay20 />
就是我那一天的<delay8 />心的顏色喔～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的我會是什麼顏色呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蠟筆呀，<delay20 />
簡簡單單就能畫出顏色，很不錯呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過要是太大力的話，
馬上就會喀地一聲斷掉，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我都很溫柔地對待它喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="031_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要說我對什麼事情最感到自豪的話……<delay20 />
大概就是我這個敏銳到<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以聞出<delay8 />任何食物的鼻子吧～！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟香味有關的困擾，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />就通通交給我吧！<delay frames="40" />
除了睡覺的時候和吃飯的時候，<delay20 />
我都可以立刻跑去幫忙喔～！！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不過，<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />到現在都還沒有人
來找我幫過忙～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你需要我幫忙嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說最近有個奇怪的傳聞<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我以前交的朋友之間<delay20 />不斷被轉述耶～<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像是說<delay20 />我自己一個人在無人島上<delay20 />
過著野外求生的生活～<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽到他們那麼說以後，<delay20 />我忍不住就說了……<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「絕對不可能啦～！<delay8 />因為我很怕鬼，<delay8 />
到現在都不敢晚上自己去上廁所耶～！！」<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果現在他們都在聊這個了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="69 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我最近<delay20 />有相當熱衷的
戶外活動喔<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="105_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是唱<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />～！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在外面大聲唱著歌，<delay20 />
感覺真舒服啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但要是嘴巴張得太大，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蟲蟲有可能會跑進嘴巴裡，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我有點怕怕的呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是模仿飛機奔跑～！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />張開雙手迎風奔跑，<delay20 />
感覺真是舒服啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有好好看路，<delay8 />
注意不要撞到人和東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以不用擔心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是邊走邊吃<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />～！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在家裡吃，<delay8 />跟在外面吃，<delay20 />
就算是一樣的食物<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />滋味也完全不同呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且就算稍微掉了屑也不要緊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />我還是有好好收拾喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="023" attrib="6a 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你很常<delay20 />看電視嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />電視上<delay8 />有很多電視節目，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就算<delay8 />看整天也不會膩喔。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="106_01" attrib="18 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有新聞<delay8 />還有綜藝節目，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />電影加電視劇<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外還有運動節目之類的對吧～</message>
	<message label="106_02" attrib="19 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且<delay8 />不只有電視節目，<delay20 />
還有各式各樣的電視廣告，<delay20 />
真的是讓人目不轉睛呢。</message>
	<message label="106_03" attrib="1a 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay20 />我之前電視沒關
就這樣入睡，<delay20 />半夜醒來時，<delay8 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發現電視畫面上有奇怪的東西喔。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="024_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是烹飪節目，<delay8 />我還會特別錄下來喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要錄下來，就不怕會錯過節目了。<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且還能要看幾遍就看幾遍呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是問答節目，<delay8 />那真的很有趣喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為就算是看過的問題，<delay8 />我也記不住答案，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以不管看幾次都很有意思呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是天氣預報，<delay8 />那可是很重要的喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟要洗衣服的話，<delay20 />果然還是會想選在
晴天時洗呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="025_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我跟你說喔，<delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可以只靠聲音
就知道是什麼電視廣告喔！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" />這是水果的廣告吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">只要看到關於購物的電視廣告，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會變得很想買，<delay20 />
感覺一不小心就會買下去呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">因為每個季節都有不同的電視廣告，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在開電視可能就只是為了看<delay8 />
這些電視廣告呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="026_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個到底<delay8 />是什麼呢～？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得那一天是<delay8 />
星期六的樣子<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個到底<delay8 />是什麼呢～？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得時間是<delay8 />
3點半的樣子<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個到底<delay8 />是什麼呢～？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得當時那狀況<delay8 />
大概維持了1分鐘左右<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="6b 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay8 />跟你說一件前陣子發生的事。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我散步的時候，<delay20 />不知道從哪裡
傳來一股很香的味道。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後我就被那股味道吸引，<delay8 />
